g Yong-hwa of CNBLUE to hold solo concert|date=4 December 2017|work=Kpop Herald}}</ref>\n\n==Awards and nominations==\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! Year\n! Award\n! Category\n! Nominated work\n! Result\n! Ref\n|-\n| 2009\n| [[2009 SBS Drama Awards|SBS Drama Awards]]\n| New Star Award\n| ''[[You're Beautiful (TV series)|You're Beautiful]]''\n| {{Won}} ||<ref>{{cite web|author=Ko Jae-wan|title=Jang Seo-hee wins grand prize at SBS Drama Awards|url=http://www.asiae.co.kr/news/view.htm?idxno=2010010415421214182|work=10Asia|accessdate=|date=4 January 2010}}</ref>\n|-\n| rowspan=\"4\"|2010\n| rowspan=\"2\"|[[Munhwa Broadcasting Corporation]]\n| Popularity Award\n| {{N/A}}\n| {{Won}} ||rowspan=2| \n|-\n| Most Popular Couple\n| We Got Married <small>(Shared with [[Seohyun]])\n| {{won}}\n|-\n| SBS Entertainment Awards\n| Best Newcomer in a Variety Show\n| ''[[The Music Trend|Inkigayo]]''\n| {{Won}} ||<ref>{{cite web|url=http://en.tenasia.com/archives/5589|title=Kang Ho-dong scores grand prize at SBS Entertainment Awards|date=31 December 2010|work=10Asia}}</ref>\n|-\n| [[3rd Korea Drama Awards]]\n| Popularity Award\n| ''[[You're Beautiful (TV series)|You're Beautiful]]''\n| {{Won}} ||<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.kdfo.org/2010_real/ko/drama/award.asp |title=Archived copy |accessdate=2011-06-02|url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120324221757/http://www.kdfo.org/2010_real/ko/drama/award.asp |archivedate=24 March 2012 }}</ref>\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\" |2011\n| 3rd [[Melon Music Awards]]\n| Music Style Best OST Song\n| <center>\"You've Fallen For Me\" (''Heartstrings'')</center>\n| {{Nom}} || \n|-\n| [[2011 MBC Drama Awards|MBC Drama Awards]]\n| Best New Actor\n| rowspan=3|''[[Heartstrings (Korean TV series)|Heartstrings]]'' \n| {{Nom}} || \n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\" |2012\n| [[48th Baeksang Arts Awards]]\n| Most Popular Actor (TV)\n| {{Nom}} || \n|-\n| [[1st K-Drama Star Awards]]\n| [[Hallyu]] Star Award\n| {{Won}} || <ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.yonhapnews.co.kr