31586038227_2&ACE_SEARCH=1|title=Jung Yong-hwa gets \u2018Voice of ELLE\u2019 award|date=21 December 2015|work=Kpop Herald}}</ref> \n|-\n| rowspan=\"3\" |2016\n| rowspan=2 |[[Seoul Music Awards]]\n| Bonsang\n| ''[[One Fine Day (Jung Yong-hwa album)|One Fine Day]]'' \n| {{nom}} \n|\n|-\n|  Popularity Award\n| {{NA}}\n| {{nom}}\n|\n|-\n| [[Golden Disc Awards]]\n| Best Solo Vocal Award\n| ''[[One Fine Day (Jung Yong-hwa album)|One Fine Day]]'' \n| {{Won}}\n| \n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\" |2018\n| rowspan=\"2\"|[[32nd Golden Disc Awards]]\n| Golden Disc Album Award\n| ''[[Do Disturb]]''\n| {{nom}}\n| <ref>{{cite web|last1=Kim|first1=Yeon-ji|script-title=ko:[32\ud68c \uace8\ub4e0] \ubd80\ubb38\ubcc4 \ud6c4\ubcf4\ubd80\ud130 \uc2ec\uc0ac\uae30\uc900\uae4c\uc9c0..\uace8\ub4e0\ub514\uc2a4\ud06c, \ud1ba\uc544\ubcf4\uae30|url=http://isplus.live.joins.com/news/article/article.asp?total_id=22191966|website=Ilgan Sports|publisher=JTBC Plus|accessdate=|language=Korean|date=11 December 2017}}</ref>\n|-\n| Global Popular Artist Award\n| {{N/A}}\n| {{nom}}\n| <ref>{{cite web|script-title=ko:\ud574\uc678 \uc2e4\uc2dc\uac04 \ud22c\ud45c|url=http://isplus.live.joins.com/goldendisc/kr/vote|website=Ilgan Sports|publisher=JTBC Plus|accessdate=|language=Korean|archiveurl=https://archive.is/20171213124018/http://isplus.live.joins.com/goldendisc/kr/vote|archivedate=2017-12-13}}</ref>\n|}\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist|30em}}\n\n==External links==\n{{commons category|Jung Yong-hwa}}\n* {{HanCinema person}}\n* {{IMDb name|4703437|Jung Yong-hwa}}\n\n{{Jung Yong-hwa}}\n{{CNBLUE}}\n\n{{Authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Jung, Yong-hwa}}\n[[Category:21st-century South Korean male actors]]\n[[Category:English-language singers from South Korea]]\n[[Category:K-pop singers]]\n[[Category:FNC Entertainment artists]]\n[[Category:Japanese-language singers of South Korea]]\n[[Category:Musicians from Busan]]\n[[Category:Singers from Seoul]]\n[[Category:South Korean male idols]]\n[[Category:South Korean male singers]]\n[[Category:South Korean male film actors]]\n[[Category:South Korean male television actors]]\n[[Category:South Korean pop guitarists]]\n[[Category:South Korean pop rock singers]]\n[[Category:South Korean radio presenters]]\n[[Category:South Korean rhythm and blues singers]]\n[[Category:South Korean rock guitarists]]\n[[Category:South Korean television presenters]]\n[[Category:CNBLUE members]]\n[[Category:South Korean singer-songwriters]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:1989 births]]\n[[Category:Jung Yong-hwa| ]]\n[[Category:Warner Music Japan artists]]\n[[Category:Male actors from Seoul]]\n", "name_user": "183.171.82.59", "label": "unsafe", "comment": "", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jung_Yong-hwa"}
{"title_page": "Andr\u00e9 Brochu", "text_new": "{{More citations needed|date=April 2018}}\n\n'''Andr\u00e9 Brochu '''(born 3 March 1942 in [[Saint-Eustache, Quebec]]) is a [[poet]], [[essay]]ist and professor of Quebecois literature.\n\n== Life ==\nHe graduated from the [[Universit\u00e9 de Montr\u00e9al]] in 1961, and from [[Paris 8 University|Universit\u00e9 Paris VIII]].<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.thecanadianencyclopedia.ca/en/article/andre-brochu/|title=Andr\u00e9 Brochu|last=Toussaint|first=Ism\u00e8ne|work=The Canadian Encyclopedia|language=en}}</ref>\n\nHe has been a member of the [[Acad\u00e9mie des lettres du Qu\u00e9bec|Acad\u00e9mie des Lettres du Qu\u00e9bec]] since September 1996.\n\n== Works ==\n\n=== Poetry ===\n* ''Privil\u00e8ges de l'ombre'', L'Hexagone, 1961\n* ''Les Matins nus, le vent'', \u00c9ditions Trois, 1989\n* ''Particuli\u00e8rement la vie change'', L'Hexagone, 1990\n* {{cite book|title = Dans les chances de l'air|publisher = \u00c9ditions de L'Hexagone|pr\u00e9nom1 = |nom1 = |pr\u00e9nom2 = |nom2 = |year = 1990|place = Montr\u00e9al, (Qu\u00e9bec), Canada|pages = [https://archive.org/details/delapoemes0000broc/page/171 171]|isbn = 978-2890065215|url = https://archive.org/details/delapoemes0000broc/page/171}}\n* {{cite book|title = Del\u00e0|publisher = \u00c9ditions de L'Hexagone|pr\u00e9nom1 = |nom1 = |pr\u00e9nom2 = |nom2 = |year = 1993|edition = 2005|place = Montr\u00e9al, (Qu\u00e9bec), Canada|pages = [https://archive.org/details/delapoemes0000broc/page/171 171]|isbn = 978-2890065215|url = https://archive.org/details/delapoemes0000broc/page/171}}\n* {{cite book|title = Tableau du po\u00e8me|publisher = \u00c9ditions XYZ|year = 1994|place = Montr\u00e9al, (Qu\u00e9bec), Canada|pages = [https://archive.org/details/tableaudupoeme0000broc/page/240 240]|isbn = 978-2-89261-115-1|url = https://archive.org/details/tableaudupoeme0000broc/page/240}}\n* ''L'Inconcevable'', \u00c9ditions Trois, 1998\n* ''Je t'aime, je t'\u00e9cris, Qu\u00e9bec-Am\u00e9rique, 2001''\n* {{cite book|title = Les Jours \u00e0 vif|publisher = \u00c9ditions Trois|volume = Opale|pr\u00e9nom1 = |nom1 = |pr\u00e9nom2 = |nom2 = |year = 2004|place = Laval, (Qu\u00e9bec), Canada|pages = [https://archive.org/details/lesjoursvifpoesi0000broc/page/109 109]|isbn = 978-2-89516-063-2|url = https://archive.org/details/lesjoursvifpoesi0000broc/page/109}}\n* ''\u00c9l\u00e9gies de lumi\u00e8re'', \u00c9ditions Trois, 2005\n* {{cite book|title = Cahiers d'Icare|publisher = \u00c9ditions Triptyque|year=  2009 |place = Montr\u00e9al, (Qu\u00e9bec), Canada|pages = 160|isbn = 978-2-89031-668-3}}\n\n=== Novels ===\n* ''Ad\u00e9odat I'', \u00c9ditions du Jour, 1973\n* {{cite book|title = La Croix du Nord|publisher = Les \u00c9ditions XYZ|pr\u00e9nom1 = |nom1 = |pr\u00e9nom2 = |nom2 = |year = 1991|edition = 2005|place = Montr\u00e9al, (Qu\u00e9bec), Canada|pages = [https://archive.org/details/dansleschancesde0000broc/page/153 153]|isbn = 978-2-89006-363-1|url = https://archive.org/details/dansleschancesde0000broc/page/153}}\n* {{cite book|title = La Vie aux trousses|publisher = Les \u00c9ditions XYZ|pr\u00e9nom1 = |nom1 = |pr\u00e9nom2 = |nom2 = |year = 1993|edition = 2005|place = Montr\u00e9al, (Qu\u00e9bec), Canada|pages = [https://archive.org/details/lavieauxtrousses0000broc/page/249 249]|isbn = 978-2-89261-073-4|url = https://archive.org/details/lavieauxtrousses0000broc/page/249}}\n* ''Fi\u00e8vres blanches'', Les \u00c9ditions XYZ, 1994\n* ''Les \u00c9pervi\u00e8res'', Les \u00c9ditions XYZ, 1996\n* ''Ad\u00e8le intime'', Les \u00c9ditions XYZ, 1996\n* ''Le Ma\u00eetre r\u00eaveur'', Les \u00c9ditions XYZ, 1997\n\n=== Essays and literary studies ===\n* ''D\u00e9lit contre d\u00e9lit'', Les Presses de l'A.G.E.U.M., 1965\n* ''Hugo : amour, crime, r\u00e9volution essai sur ''Les Mis\u00e9rables, Presses de l'Universit\u00e9 de Montr\u00e9al, 1974 ; r\u00e9\u00e9dition, Nota Bene, 1999\n* ''L'\u00c9vasion tragique : essai sur les romans d'Andr\u00e9 Langevin'', HMH Hurtubuse, 1985\n* {{cite book|title = La Vis\u00e9e critique|chapter = Essais autobiographiques et litt\u00e9raires|publisher = \u00c9ditions du Bor\u00e9al|year = 1988|place = Montr\u00e9al, (Qu\u00e9bec), Canada|pages = [https://archive.org/details/laviseecritiquee0000broc/page/249 249]|isbn = 978-2-89052-229-9|url-access = registration|url = https://archive.org/details/laviseecritiquee0000broc/page/249}}\n* ''Le Singulier pluriel'', L'Hexagone, 1992\n* ''La Grande Langue : \u00e9loge de l'anglais'', Les \u00c9ditions XYZ, 1993\n* ''L'Institut Rossell (1934-1994), Les \u00c9ditions XYZ, 1994''\n* ''Roman et \u00e9num\u00e9ration de Flaubert \u00e0 Perec'', D\u00e9partement d'\u00e9tudes fran\u00e7aises de l'Universit\u00e9 de Montr\u00e9al, 1996\n* ''Une \u00e9tude de ''Bonheur d'occasion, Bor\u00e9al, 1998\n* ''Saint-Denys Garneau, le po\u00e8te'', Les \u00c9ditions XYZ, 1999\n* ''Anne H\u00e9bert : le secret de vie et de mort'', Presses de l'Universit\u00e9 d'Ottawa, 2000\n\n== Honors ==\n* 1988 \u2013 Prix Gabrielle-Roy, ''La Vis\u00e9e critique''\n* 1990 \u2013 2e prix du Concours de nouvelles de Radio-Canada, ''L'Esprit ailleurs''\n* 1990 \u2013 [[1990 Governor General's Awards|Prix du Gouverneur g\u00e9n\u00e9ral]], ''Dans les chances de l'air''\n* 1991 \u2013 [[1991 Governor General's Awards|Prix du Gouverneur g\u00e9n\u00e9ral]], ''La Croix du Nord''\n* 1993 \u2013 Prix litt\u00e9raires du Journal de Montr\u00e9al, ''La Vie aux trousses''\n* 1995 \u2013 Grand Prix du Festival international de la po\u00e9sie, ''Del\u00e0''\n* 1996 \u2013 ''Membre'' de l'[[Acad\u00e9mie des lettres du Qu\u00e9bec]]\n* 2004 \u2013 [[2004 Governor General's Awards|Prix du Gouverneur g\u00e9n\u00e9ral]], ''Les Jours \u00e0 vif''\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n== External links ==\n* [http://auteurs.contemporain.info/andre-brochu/ Documentation critique sur l'\u0153uvre d'Andr\u00e9 Brochu (Site auteurs.contemporain.info)]\n* [http://www.erudit.org/revue/vi/1995/v20/n3/201192ar.pdf Bibliographie compl\u00e8te de l'auteur]\n\n{{authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Brochu, Andre}}\n[[Category:Governor General's Award-winning fiction writers]]\n[[Category:Universit\u00e9 de Montr\u00e9al faculty]]\n[[Category:Writers from Quebec]]\n[[Category:People from Saint-Eustache, Quebec]]\n[[Category:Universit\u00e9 de Montr\u00e9al alumni]]\n[[Category:Canadian poets in French]]\n[[Category:Canadian male poets]]\n[[Category:Canadian male novelists]]\n[[Category:Canadian novelists in French]]\n[[Category:20th-century Canadian novelists]]\n[[Category:20th-century Canadian poets]]\n[[Category:20th-century Canadian male writers]]\n[[Category:Governor General's Award-winning poets]]\n[[Category:1942 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:20th-century Canadian essayists]]\n[[Category:Canadian male non-fiction writers]]\n", "text_old": "{{More citations needed|date=April 2018}}\n\n'''Andr\u00e9 Brochu '''(born 3 March 1942 in [[Saint-Eustache, Quebec]]) is a [[poet]], [[essay]]ist and professor of Quebecois literature.\n\n== Life ==\nHe graduated from the [[Universit\u00e9 de Montr\u00e9al]] in 1961, and from [[Paris 8 University|Universit\u00e9 Paris VIII]].<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.thecanadianencyclopedia.ca/en/article/andre-brochu/|title=Andr\u00e9 Brochu|last=Toussaint|first=Ism\u00e8ne|work=The Canadian Encyclopedia|language=en}}</ref>\n\nHe has been a member of the [[Acad\u00e9mie des lettres du Qu\u00e9bec|Acad\u00e9mie des Lettres du Qu\u00e9bec]] since September 1996.\n\n== Works ==\n\n=== Poetry ===\n* ''Privil\u00e8ges de l'ombre'', L'Hexagone, 1961\n* ''Les Matins nus, le vent'', \u00c9ditions Trois, 1989\n* ''Particuli\u00e8rement la vie change'', L'Hexagone, 1990\n* {{cite book|title = Dans les chances de l'air|publisher = \u00c9ditions de L'Hexagone|pr\u00e9nom1 = |nom1 = |pr\u00e9nom2 = |nom2 = |year = 1990|place = Montr\u00e9al, (Qu\u00e9bec), Canada|pages = [https://archive.org/details/delapoemes0000broc/page/171 171]|isbn = 978-2890065215|url = https://archive.org/details/delapoemes0000broc/page/171}}\n* {{cite book|title = Del\u00e0|publisher = \u00c9ditions de L'Hexagone|pr\u00e9nom1 = |nom1 = |pr\u00e9nom2 = |nom2 = |year = 1993|edition = 2005|place = Montr\u00e9al, (Qu\u00e9bec), Canada|pages = [https://archive.org/details/delapoemes0000broc/page/171 171]|isbn = 978-2890065215|url = https://archive.org/details/delapoemes0000broc/page/171}}\n* {{cite book|title = Tableau du po\u00e8me|publisher = \u00c9ditions XYZ|year = 1994|place = Montr\u00e9al, (Qu\u00e9bec), Canada|pages = [https://archive.org/details/tableaudupoeme0000broc/page/240 240]|isbn = 978-2-89261-115-1|url = https://archive.org/details/tableaudupoeme0000broc/page/240}}\n* ''L'Inconcevable'', \u00c9ditions Trois, 1998\n* ''Je t'aime, je t'\u00e9cris, Qu\u00e9bec-Am\u00e9rique, 2001''\n* {{cite book|title = Les Jours \u00e0 vif|publisher = \u00c9ditions Trois|volume = Opale|pr\u00e9nom1 = |nom1 = |pr\u00e9nom2 = |nom2 = |year = 2004|place = Laval, (Qu\u00e9bec), Canada|pages = [https://archive.org/details/lesjoursvifpoesi0000broc/page/109 109]|isbn = 978-2-89516-063-2|url = https://archive.org/details/lesjoursvifpoesi0000broc/page/109}}\n* ''\u00c9l\u00e9gies de lumi\u00e8re'', \u00c9ditions Trois, 2005\n* {{cite book|title = Cahiers d'Icare|publisher = \u00c9ditions Triptyque|year=  2009 |place = Montr\u00e9al, (Qu\u00e9bec), Canada|pages = 160|isbn = 978-2-89031-668-3}}\n\n=== Novels ===\n* ''Ad\u00e9odat I'', \u00c9ditions du Jour, 1973\n* {{cite book|title = La Croix du Nord|publisher = Les \u00c9ditions XYZ|pr\u00e9nom1 = |nom1 = |pr\u00e9nom2 = |nom2 = |year = 1991|edition = 2005|place = Montr\u00e9al, (Qu\u00e9bec), Canada|pages = [https://archive.org/details/dansleschancesde0000broc/page/153 153]|isbn = 978-2-89006-363-1|url = https://archive.org/details/dansleschancesde0000broc/page/153}}\n* {{cite book|title = La Vie aux trousses|publisher = Les \u00c9ditions XYZ|pr\u00e9nom1 = |nom1 =